{"tid":140414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]結婚僅一年　女教師捅死丈夫後墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-03-02T07:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T08:07:52.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a229ebaa0fe21b1d90aafd3a883000d66f67717d","tid":140414,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/bkncn-20170302134549874-0302_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fbkncn-20170302134549874-0302_05011_001.html&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4813b5b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/bkncn-20170302134549874-0302_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n陝西延安發生倫常血案！延安市實驗中學一名女教師昨晚捅死丈夫後墮樓身亡。當地警方目前仍在調查具體原因。<br />\n<br />\n延安實驗中學負責人稱，涉事女教師在延安實驗中學任教，其張姓丈夫之前亦在該校任教，事發前被借調，兩人於一年前結婚。另有知情人士透露，該女教師的丈夫剛被市教育局借調為辦公室副主任，案發當晚女教師捅了丈夫11刀致死，然後從當地的御城大廈22樓墮至5樓平台死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n雙喜臨門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3441a2a74b27d269c44275acf75a204806bdf94","tid":140414,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"做咩呀你？"}]}